Name:           ros-noetic-rosserial-xbee
Version:        0.9.2
Release:        1%{?dist}%{?release_suffix}
Summary:        ROS rosserial_xbee package

License:        BSD
URL:            http://ros.org/wiki/rosserial_xbee
